bre select hotels corp
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: REIT
BRE Select Hotels Corporation operates as a non-listed real estate investment trust. The Company provides investment, ownership, management, as well as hotels related services which includes guestrooms facilities. BRE Select Hotels serves its clients in the State of New York.




