BRE Select Hotels Corp.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 1:57 PM ET
Equity Real Estate Investment Trusts (REITs)

Company Overview of BRE Select Hotels Corp.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
BRE Select Hotels Corp. is a real estate investment trust. The firm invests in the real estate markets of United States. It focuses on ownership of upscale, extended-stay and select-service hotels. BRE Select Hotels Corp. was formed on November 28, 2012 and is based in New York, New York. BRE Select Hotels Corp. operates as a subsidiary of Blackstone Real Estate Advisors.


345 Park AvenueNew York, NY 10154United StatesFounded in 2012



Phone: 212-583-5000

www.bre-select-hotels.com







